                            <p>Students from Sweden: The Swedish student grant system CSN has recognised ADK , therefore Swedish students can receive funds. <a class="external-link" href="http://www.csn.se/">For details please ask CSN! </a></p>
                            <h3 class="visualClear">What makes us different?</h3>
                            <p class=" ">We are a family of professional linguists and teachers and feel that we understand better than most the difficulties you face using German at work and in your free time. We are also personally involved in the school at every level – a degree of commitment which is feasible in a school of our size.  Our methods are the best there are for learning German in a fast and effivient way. Our staff and teachers will make your stay at Augsburger Deutschkurse an experience to remember, one that will prove invaluable to your future.  In our so called family business, all our teachers work with us for many years, are experienced and dispose of a relevant University degree. Our students are near to our heart, we are available at any time.</p>
                            <p>Unbureaucratic, flexible and individual – this is our service and something which makes us so special and distinguishes us from other schools.<br />Our modern methods are effective and up-to-date, we make an effort to organize your stay as pleasant as possible – an experience which you will remember!</p>
